I have polished the barrel ramp and put about 300 rounds through it most of which were self defense rounds. It’s role for my wife’s first conceal carry so reliablity was paramount, no printing here. The coolest thing about this gun is it as comfortable to shoot on the range so practice is fun. Great gun for entry into conceal carry. Wife is moving up to 9mm and higher capacity, this gun built her confidence. This version may be the nicest that Sig makes in the 238 with the  polished and engraved slide and the Sig medallions in the grips and the Sig night sights. If you have any questions just email me. Included are 2 flush fitting magazines and one extended , a DeSantis IWB leather holster and the Sig OWB kydex holster, case,lock and paperwork.
